In all 1,177 Barrio 18 gang members were transferred from Izalco jail to San Francisco Gotera in an effort to curb gang violence .
They will mix with rivals from the hyper-violent Mara Salvatrucha gang, or MS-13 .
In a potentially incendiary move, they will all be classified not by their gang affiliation, but by how dangerous they are .
The policy of mixing the gangs together came about when officials realised gangs were directing criminal activity from behind bars .